metadata.description:
For more than a year I have been working on various arts on fx(hash). I can point out a few positive aspects: I work more and more, I constantly experiment, I get more and more pleasure from the programming process itself. But I also note that the back felt this year. It became impossible to sit continuously on a chair for 8-10 hours. I feel that it is necessary to connect physical exercises.

This experimental work contains:
-different light position;
-different colors;
-different view;
-different position.

Made with p5.js
Color palette by Jam3
